com.bham.bd.view

Class MenuSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bham.bd.view.MenuSession

  • public class MenuSession
extends Object

    Menu Session

    This class manages all the menus. Not only it sets up a stage for the main menu, it also is responsible for bringing up pause menu and end screen during the gameplay. Therefore, it has a strong communication with GameSession.

      • createGameSession

        public void createGameSession(GameFlowEvent e)
        Handles the event of starting the game

        Creates a single Game Session based on the chosen parameters. The parameters can be the number of players, type of map and the game mode. Currently only 1 player and survival mode is supported.

        Parameters:
        e - event from which the parameters of a new game session are checked
